Haak Human Origins analysis: Model 1

Kushal K Dey, Hussein Al Asadi

September 13, 2015

We present the results of fitting ancient Sructure (Model 1 ) on Haak Human Origins on a total of 403 samples and around 300,000 SNPs. We ran two set ups

K_Known=3 K_Unknown=0

K_Known=3 K_Unknown=1

K_Known=3 K_Unknown=2
